<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | Blog Page</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
        }
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
          
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        }
        .about-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .about-desc {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .about-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            min-width: 220px;
            flex: 1 1 220px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-card i {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .about-card h3 {
            margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .about-card p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .about-footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-title">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt"></i> About This Blog
        </div>
        <div class="about-desc">
            Welcome to <strong>Your Blog Name</strong>!<br>
            This is a space where ideas, stories, and inspiration come together. Whether you're here to read, write, or connect, our mission is to make sharing thoughts easy and enjoyable for everyone.
        </div>
        <div class="about-details">
            <div class="about-card">
                <i class="fas fa-user-edit"></i>
                <h3>Who Am I?</h3>
                <p>
                    Hi, I'm Kaushal, a passionate web developer and lifelong learner. I created this blog to share knowledge, spark creativity, and connect with like-minded people.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card">
                <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>
                    To empower everyone to express themselves, learn from others, and build a positive online community through thoughtful blogging.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-card">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
                <p>
                    Built with Node.js, Express, and EJS. Designed for simplicity, speed, and a great user experience.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-footer">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact: <a href="mailto:kaushakohli08@gmail.com">kaushalkohli08@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>